Name: Without End
About the game: Without End is a story heavy, turn based, experimental RPG, following the every day life of a high schooler and his friends. Features: -An engaging short (5-6 hour) story -Decisions with weight, causing the world to evolve -High replayability with multiple endings -Unique enemies who remember your actions -Bad jokes (in case you don't like good ones) -5 memorable party members with unique skills and play styles This game involves mental health and may not be suitable for people with trauma or suicidal inclinations.
